data.description: When you walk through the door of this gem you will feel right at home.  This 4 bedroom 2.1 bath home boasts a beautiful open floor plan perfect for entertaining.  This updated kitchen with granite and stainless appliances opens into a spacious family and dining room.  Step out onto the private deck and take in the beauty of the private, wooded backyard.  The beautifully updated master suite is just what your most discerning buyers have been looking for.  Don’t miss this one - it won’t last long!
